title: You dont have to get fed to win games in league.
body:
You just have to not feed. 

Now hopefully i can follow my own advice as a i stream! 

Come say hi! 

But really do so, I feel lonely!

https://www.twitch.tv/kingspadeix

replies.body: the problem is, though, people aren't here to win the games. They're here to get fed and feel good about themselves, myself included.
